{"tid":2508607,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"最自由的作者！《獵人》冨樫義博疑漫畫家辭職，最新狀態寫上「無業人士」！","createTime":"2021-04-29T01:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T02:11:44.000Z","uid":47272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe76059beab078cac5323e1621b20c51287384e8","tid":2508607,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.juksy.com/archives/108267?utm_content=link&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=fb_juksy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F108267%3Futm_content%3Dlink%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfb_juksy&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzaNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=fd9daa8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.juksy.com/archives/108267?utm_content=link&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=fb_juksy</a><br />\n日本漫畫家冨樫義博在 1998 年開始連載的少年漫畫作品《HUNTER&times;HUNTER》，由於後段作者不斷休刊拖稿而成為了網友惡搞名哏：《獵人》只有第 3？日本票選「死前絕對想追完的動漫排行榜」，酷拉皮卡好想下船⋯。不過光是《獵人》的花式周邊和活動，人稱「富奸」 的冨樫義博，在昨天 4 月 27 日時剛滿 55 歲生日，卻意外透露自己已經從漫畫家這一行辭職？！<br />\n原來《獵人》作者冨樫義博最近撰寫了文字評論，描述自己對於武論尊原作、原哲夫作畫的日經典漫畫《北斗神拳》的尊敬和熱愛、感謝之意。不過引起日本網友暴動的是，可以看見在最後冨樫義博將自己署名為「無職」，說明自己只是一介住在東京都的無業人士，而不再是漫畫家這個頭銜。延伸閱讀：國外玩起絕望造句：「等疫情結束那一天⋯聽起來就像等《獵人》復刊一樣遙遙無期」！<br />\n「冨樫義博 無業人士」這個關鍵字立刻在日本推特飆升為人氣討論話題，尤其是《獵人》迷都紛紛對於富奸自稱是無業人士大感傻眼，所以我們真的永遠看不到酷拉皮卡下船了嗎？也有網友幽默引用《進擊的巨人》段子：「冨樫義博，你是最自由的漫畫家。」、「靠獵人、幽遊白書和老婆的美少女戰士，他一輩子都可以躺著打電動了」、「自稱無業人士，日本漫畫史上第一人」、「他根本是來報復社會的」、「酷拉皮卡：到底是游泳比較快，還是船開得快？」、「我死後記得燒獵人結局給我」。亦可延伸閱讀：日本老爸推薦鬼滅迷女兒看《獵人》，小孩入迷興奮問：最新一話下個月就會出嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQyP79a6VwtFneGK4Z2E8Ms7jKApASDv5twevFUT4rNkG?filename=Rx2Bakv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx2Bakv.jpg&h=8f36f494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"207c5d448692a0f8a5aa28b3d86321d65cc45f0a","tid":2508607,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"都成55 仲畫乜鳩<br />\n靠收版權稅都發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時好似巨人咁爛尾 比人屌得仲甘"},{"pid":"466eb40ea936a4848cceaae573da9c01325bd823","tid":2508607,"uid":197857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇啦冇啦<br />\n可以出文字版架"},{"pid":"dba049ed80310e9f3d6baf46b0e607504ebf7295","tid":2508607,"uid":250773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"207c5d448692a0f8a5aa28b3d86321d65cc45f0a","tid":2508607,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"都成55 仲畫乜鳩<br />\n靠收版權稅都發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時好似巨人咁爛尾 比人屌得仲甘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:46:16.000Z","msg":"冇尾vs爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd39f9b04ac275790e980558092dd2b3f5e8b59","tid":2508607,"uid":145635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"個老豆陰9個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05903735355d65f1ea42083c43e24f159b481b42","tid":2508607,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"同GOT一樣<br />\n俾個結局我已滿足<br />\n邊個製作唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b861277e3345642d4090c479b58ddd5a8d59159","tid":2508607,"uid":326700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"無職轉生～到了異世界就拿出真本事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嚟睇真本事"},{"pid":"4a8f2